@startuml
!include ../_style/puml.style
left to right direction

actor Instructor

package "Analytics Dashboard <<System>>" {
  rectangle "Authentication" as Auth
  rectangle "Data Visualization Engine" as Viz
  rectangle "Filtering Module" as Filter
  rectangle "Insight Generator" as Insights
  rectangle "Report Export Module" as Export
}

Instructor --> Auth : Login
Auth --> Viz : Display Analytics
Instructor --> Filter : Apply Filters
Filter --> Viz : Adjust Visualizations
Instructor --> Insights : Review Suggested Insights
Instructor --> Export : Save/Export Report
Export --> Instructor : Report/CSV

note right of Insights
Detects attention drops,
provides suggested insights
for teaching or research
end note
@enduml